title: Kaptur, a veteran Democrat, defeats Majewski in an Ohio congressional race.
description: Marcy Kaptur, the 20-term Democratic congresswoman, won re-election against J.R. Majewski, a far-right Air Force veteran who was found to have misled voters about his service.
dc:creator: Catie Edmondson

media:content.media:description: Representative Marcy Kaptur at the Capitol in September.
